name: Farty Rocket V 0.2.0
description:
Click, space or up arrow to make the player jump. Don't touch the spikes object to change the score. Have 9 skins of players.

This game was inspired by one of Dani's games, the link is over here:-

https://danidev.itch.io/farty-rocket
